<text ID="INV-2dc58b17-7bea-4408-b092-790b424ed7da"><paragraph ID="INV-1f6e9e82-cbc3-4036-bc05-50912c71eb32">Shake well. Apply to the affected areas and rub in thoroughly. Use twice daily or as directed by a physician.</paragraph></text>
